      "properties": {"Node name for S&R": "Note"},
      "widgets_values": ["LATENTSYNC 1.6 LIP-SYNC PASS\n=========================================\n\nNode chain:\n  VHS_LoadVideo → VideoLengthAdjuster → LatentSyncNode → VHS_VideoCombine\n  LoadAudio ↗                ↗\n\nLatentSyncNode parameters:\n- seed: 42 (reproducibility)\n- lips_expression: 1.5 (1.0=subtle, 2.0+=expressive)\n- inference_steps: 20 (10=fast, 30-50=best quality)\n\nVideoLengthAdjuster:\n- mode: 'normal' (pads audio with silence, trims video to match)\n- fps: 25 (must match VHS_LoadVideo force_rate)\n- silent_padding_sec: 0.5\n\nINPUTS:\n- video: base singer MP4 from workflow 01/02\n- audio: isolated vocal segment (16kHz mono WAV)\n  NOT the full Suno mix — that would sync to instruments\n\nOUTPUT:\n- lip-synced MP4 at 25fps with muxed audio\n\nVRAM: ~10GB peak at 512x512 (safe on 16GB)\nSPEED: ~1 min per 5s clip on RTX 4090 mobile"],
